query_blocking_template

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_blocking_template -  Find the template to use for the area blocked by an obstacle.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string * query_blocking_template(int x,
int y,
int type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^x%^RESET%^ - the x co-ordinate of the blockage
%^BOLD%^y%^RESET%^ - the y co-ordinate of the blockage
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type is 0 for normal, 1 for straight, 2 for diagonal

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/world_map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Find the template to use for the area blocked by an obstacle.
This will do nifty template fitting stuff for obstacles.
.EP

